Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被喜歡的女生叫出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:26.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,肯定是表白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:30.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:45.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都快十分鐘了 還沒拿出勇氣來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:52.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高 高瀨你 喜歡的人什麼的 有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:56.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種場合要怎麼回答才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說「你這傢伙」是不是比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但這樣的話不就搶了她的表白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以還是只能說沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼?有嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:08.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:10.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤?聽不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有的話就說有不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:13.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就 那就沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就 是什麼鬼啊 你說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有就是沒有的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:18.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你不是有話要跟我說才叫我出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:22.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所 所以說…啊對了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我就是想問一下你有沒有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,然後呢 問了之後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事了的話我就回去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也不是沒事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是今天時機不是很…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我先回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:58.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那個… 請…和我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好樣的 說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明 明天也可以見個面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是要我來說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:13.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明 明天就會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 可以啦 但是在這之前我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:23.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 明天會見我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:31.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天抱歉啊 想要說的事情都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:36.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 關於這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:46.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明天會好好說喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就明天見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:03.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,班委皆川同學沒有在好好幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川同學 稍微幫我一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸 但是很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼要當班委啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡古屋君呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能不能不要捉弄我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊啦 生氣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對不起 我沒有要惹你生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並 並不是在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是說喜歡你是真的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是表白的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:42.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然 可以跟我交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:46.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是傳聞皆川你和好多男生在一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我是處女唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:54.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且 雖然有男性朋友 但是並不是那種關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你在懷疑嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你覺得我是和誰都會睡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並 並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你肯定在想像我做H的事情的場景 真是苦惱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:09.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才沒有! 果然只是在逗我玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 但是這種事情不是很難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我才不知道你是不是認真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我認真的說出來你會好好回答我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,回 回答什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:25.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我對皆川同學還不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底為什麼是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:29.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川的話其他更好的也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:29.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那古屋君呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:40.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 我還不太懂怎麼交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你在笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:50.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為古屋君很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不聊這個話題了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦?還沒聽到回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我要是回答你了 肯定又會被笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:58.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊啊 開始討厭我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是啊 討厭你亂開玩笑這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那拒絕我不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說了這個話題…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看來也未必呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是討厭!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被不吸菸的學生會長發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,切 真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這樣可不行啊梶同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,赤木 你這傢伙準備給老師告狀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不 我也沒那麼壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這回就原諒你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這不是講得通道理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果你和我接吻的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你是在小看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是在說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,事實上我一直有個煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我至今為止一直沒有喜歡的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤? 不是因為是同性戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不勞您費心 這我已經試驗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 你試驗什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我僅僅是對女性沒有興趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不知道交往之後要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以就想接吻一下試試?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好啊 聽起來挺有趣不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就讓我來教教你怎麼接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不 我知道怎麼接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,意外的挺配合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也還好 反正也不是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只要有錢的話和誰做都沒關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:24.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嗎? 那你多少錢能賣個身呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,十萬左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,正好十萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,帶這麼多錢什麼鬼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:30.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在害怕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤!? 才沒有害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實啊 你沒有援交的經驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤!? 少小看我!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,通常 要不了十萬的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這就證明了你沒有過經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 其實我覺得十萬還是太便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我希望梶同學能多珍重一下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,赤木…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 雖然吻還是要接的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還要做啊你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,當然啊 抽菸那件事還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是害怕嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:10.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 上了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一股焦油臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你好臭啊 梶同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼啊! 這也沒辦法的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你還是別抽菸了比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好囉嗦啊! 你是我男朋友嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這也 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我感覺 我喜歡上梶同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果你能戒掉煙的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,去死!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,三年級的湯川前輩 明天就要畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩 今晚也去看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不要 笹原你太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:09.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好過分 難得我還準備表個白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這是第幾百次說這話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦～ 暴露了嗎～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:13.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我有一個壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,總喜歡把自己真實的感情糊弄過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這次一定要認認真真的 把自己的感情傳達給前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,首先 最重要的是營造氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:33.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩 今晚好冷 我靠你身邊行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 別妨礙到我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,順便推倒一下也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:40.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:42.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在這裡觀星也是最後一次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:49.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和學長一起看星星 這也是最後一次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:50.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是願意的話以後也可以一起看就是了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好吵啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笹原你 還記得星星的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:03.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!? 這個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,角宿一 之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是我最開始告訴你的星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只有前輩告訴我的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我才能不忘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你把角宿一指給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!? 啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:22.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好好幹啊 明年就只剩你一個部員了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:26.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是前輩的錯唷 總是一副嚇人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 你為什麼進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是的 肯定是因為愛啊 愛!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是的是的 能被後輩愛著 我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:44.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那 那要是我真的喜歡你 你會開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:47.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有糊弄說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,湯川前輩會開心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然還是不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 這個氛圍是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我弄錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,做過頭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是吧不是吧不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笹原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的! 你當真啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,又搞砸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,以後再也表不成白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說了也不會信我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和前輩在一起的這兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然我說了很多次喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一次也沒認真的表白過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}前輩已經要畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我再也沒有傳達自己感情的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}想哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}才不想在前輩面前哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不想讓他擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不想把氣氛弄僵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}還想像往常一樣愉快的笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要哭不要哭不要哭不要哭不要哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:48.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要哭了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你的「喜歡」已經聽膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}咦!? 好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是 今夜是最後一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:04.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在我離校前還想再聽一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你說不出口的話就由我來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}前輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}超喜歡你的～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}別哭啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 春
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也會覺得很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}此時此刻也在想念著你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}喜歡與討厭相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的機率的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}還是跨不出這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們的關係可以說是曖昧模糊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雖然無聊但還是希望能感受到屬於我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要珍視這份感情
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.17,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.34,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.85,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.68,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.14,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:51.52,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.95,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:03.49,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.67,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:14.55,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:20.64,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:32.17,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}逐漸淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.34,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:39.85,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}害怕這逐漸的  忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.68,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.14,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想把這份風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:51.52,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}鎖進我的心裡  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:56.95,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想與你相見這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:03.49,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}卻很需要勇氣  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.67,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:14.55,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明天當我  睜開眼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:20.64,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你能在我身旁而已
